LINE.Text: Continued focus on supply chain improvements at ITC not only
enhances market servicing but also generates significant livelihood
opportunities. Substantial investments have been made in
augmenting distribution infrastructure to support a larger scale of
operations in the wake of growing volumes and to ensure the
competitiveness of ITC's brands in the market place. Leveraging its
